{"tid":2223186,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"CLC莊錠欣Elkie文化節任MC以廣東話主持開幕公演","createTime":"2020-09-29T15:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T16:14:06.000Z","uid":365024,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"82be84213b581feb3a70d02501efbe8531942f5b","tid":2223186,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T15:32:00.000Z","msg":"韓國十月文化節2020<br />\n-<br />\nCLC 成員 Elkie 莊錠欣 將擔任特別MC，以廣東話主持開幕公演。<br />\n-<br />\n由駐香港韓國文化院及大韓民國駐香港總領事館合辦的第10屆韓國十月文化節，今年以「同行」(Better Together) 作為主題，於10月至11月期間舉行逾20場的線上活動，包括表演、展覽、韓食及電影等，文化節特地以「同行」(Better Together)為主題，答謝香港大眾一直以來對韓國文化的熱愛,為受疫情影響的香港市民打氣。<br />\n-<br />\n10月3日開幕公演將於YouTube直播，國立國樂管弦樂團將會演奏二胡協奏曲《香》、《太極旗飄揚》 主題曲 &ldquo;Epilogue&rdquo;及《南道阿里郎》等一系列韓國曲目，而且更特地準備了「香港流行金曲串燒」，令香港觀眾可以一飽耳福！<br />\n-<br />\n開幕公演日期時間<br />\n10月3日下午3點<br />\n<br />\n直播平台 YOUTUBE : 駐香港韓國文化院  <a href=\"https://youtu.be/va-3QW3YbME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fva-3QW3YbME&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWK2paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=a2c5cd17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/va-3QW3YbME</a><br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">◆ ◇ ◆ ◇ ◆ ◇ ◆ ◇ ◆ ◇ ◆ ◇ ◆ ◇ ◆ ◇ ◆ ◇ ◆ ◇ ◆ ◇ <br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n▹ Facebook &bull; Instagram  @hk.kpop.page<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5f3de5d0c1676286de89bff8b070f0249ebdb9a1","tid":2223186,"uid":11156,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af02a7652df9b37d5f1787cadb3936db54483631","tid":2223186,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"D表演節目見到都想訓.."},{"pid":"6aa812d238d69cd14cea21922ce50a30ebcaf35a","tid":2223186,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:18:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"087517e7975260401e8c04a99a031a26c1c5d0b8","tid":2223186,"uid":28743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6aa